extends layout

block content
    .page.js-page
      // One Page Sidebar
      .one-page-sidebar
        // One Page Sidebar Header
        .one-page-sidebar-header
          // One Page Logo
          .one-page-logo
            // Logo Image
            a.logo-image(href='/employees')
              img(src='/images/logo2.png')
            br
            a.logo-image(href='/employees')
              img(src='/images/employee.png')
            // End of Logo Image
          // End of One Page Logo
          // One Page Meta
          // End of One Page Meta
        // End of One Page Sidebar Header
        // One Page Nav
        .one-page-nav-wrapper.js-custom-scrollbar
          ul.one-page-nav.js-one-page-nav(data-prepend-to='.js-prepend-mobile-menu')
            li
              a(href='#gifts')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-gift
                | Gifts
            li
              a(href='#points_and_badges')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-id-badge
                | Points & Badges
            li
              a(href='#why')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-question
                | Why SkilledTree assign badge for me?
            li
              a(href='#points')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-check
                | Points And Rewards
            li
              a(href='#type')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-cog
                | Type of Badges and its Points
            li
              a(href='#activities')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-blind
                | Activities and Points
        // End of One Page Nav
        // One Page Sidebar Footer
        footer.one-page-sidebar-footer
          | All Rights Reserved.
          a(href='http://www.masymbol.com/', target='_blank') Masymbol Technologies
          |  Pvt Ltd © 2016
        // End of One Page Sidebar Footer
      // End of One Page Sidebar
      // One Page Content
      .one-page-content
        // Header
        header.header.large.header-one-page.js-header-fixed
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .row
              .col-md-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-5
                .visible-sm-block.visible-xs-block
                  // Logo Image
                  a.logo-image(href='/')
                    img.img-responsive(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/skilledtree-public/logo.png', alt='logo')
                  // End of Logo Image
              .col-md-12.col-sm-6.col-xs-7
                // Menu
                nav.right.helper
                  ul.menu.sf-menu.js-menu
                    li
                      a(href='/employees')
                        i.fa.fa-home.fa-lg
                    li
                      a(href='/employees/introduction') Introduction 
                    li
                      a.active(href='/employees/points_and_gifts') Points & Gifts
                    li
                      a(href='/employees/friends') Friends 
                    li
                      a(href='/employees/jobs') Jobs
                    li
                      a(href='/employees/resumes') Resumes 
                    li
                      a(href='/employees/header') Header
                    li
                      a(href='/employees/dashboard')
                        | Dashboard
                // End of Menu
        // End of Header
        #content
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .col-md-12
              #gifts.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1 Gifts
                p.category-content
                  | SkilledTree will assign few referral gifts to each company account by default. These referral gifts are fully customizable by your HR manager. 
                  br
                  |  You will be getting the rewards incase your friends gets selected in the organization. Referral reward for each job will be decided by your company. And that will be processed by the corresponding HRs. You can track your referral reward status in the ‘Dashboard’.
            br
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/referral2.png', width='100%')
            br
            br
            .col-md-12
              #points_and_badges.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1 Points & Badges
                p.category-content
                  | SkilledTree automatically track your referral activities, based your activities you will receive badges.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/points.png', width='100%')
            br
            br
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/badges.png', width='100%')
            br
            br
            .col-md-12
              #why.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1 Why SkilledTree assign badge for me?
                p.category-content
                  | The jobs which are posted by the employers in your team will be visible in your jobs wall. You can add your friends who are seeking the jobs or any working professionals to SkilledTree by uploading their personal information such as Name, Email or Phone number in an Excel format or by adding them manually. Those jobs will be reachable to them in their Jobs wall. Else, you can share those jobs with any of your Social Media accounts such as Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Pinterest and Google plus.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #points.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1
                  | Points & Reward
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | Total number of points you have earned by performing various company activities such as Friends Connection, Upload Resume, Social Media Integration etc.,
            .col-md-12
              #type.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Type of Badges and Points
                p.category-content
                  | Bulk Points will be added to you if you refer any of your friends for the suitable job which was posted by uploading their resume in the ‘Resumes’ section.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/badges2.png', width='100%')
            br
            br
            .col-md-12
              #activities.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                br
                h1
                  | Activities and Points
                p.category-content
                  | Points will vary for each company but you can view the simple structure of activities and its points here.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/activties.png', width='100%')
      // End of One Page Content
